client.gamestate

Class GameState

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.gamestate.GameState
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DiscardingState, FirstRoundState, IsNotTurnState, PlayingState, RobbingState, RollingState, SecondRoundState

    public abstract class GameState
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract class of states the player and game is in. By default, all non-overrided can-dos return false and actions throw an error.
